<p>The diagram shows that Data Science really needs a combination of three skill-sets: <a href="#hacking-skills">Hacking Skills</a>, <a href="#math-and-statistics-knowledge">Math and Statistics Knowledge</a>, and <a href="#substantive-expertise">Substantive Expertise</a>.
True Data Science would be where these three disciplines intersect:</p>

<p align="center">
  <img alt="img-name" src="/assets/img/blog/Data_Science_VD2.jpg" width="410" />
  <br />
    <em>Real Data Science</em>
</p>

