<p>Drew Conway, Co-author of Machine Learning for Hackers <sup id="fnref:1" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:1" class="footnote">1</a></sup>, makes special mention of what he calls
the <a href="#danger-zone">Danger Zone</a>, or where he classifies people who know “enough to be dangerous”:</p>

<p align="center">
  <img alt="img-name" src="/assets/img/blog/Data_Science_VD3.jpg" width="410" />
  <br />
    <em>The "Danger Zone"</em>
</p>

